{"tid":2256651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林文龍揸旗專攻網上節目 搵達哥開枱打牌","createTime":"2020-10-24T13:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T14:16:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07a4d44de628827b6744df8c8e5110bdceef332d","tid":2256651,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"林文龍開設新節目《今晚有牌打》節目，與打機達人達哥一起做打牌節目，約嘉賓進行網上直播打麻雀，二人今日在亞視總台見記者，林文龍表示節目中觀眾可給意見，最後會得到獎品。他笑言自己平時有打牌，朋友間稱他做「儍強」：「但我有時儍唔晒，有清醒嘅時候，藥力發作會強勁。」暫時會拍4集作試金石，嘉賓方面仍接洽中，但沒打算邀請太太郭可盈出席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201023/OE3DVM6UYJE7NDWKYU76Z3HL5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201023%2FOE3DVM6UYJE7NDWKYU76Z3HL5U%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=2e424ecb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201023%2FOE3DVM6UYJE7NDWKYU76Z3HL5U%2F&h=f0f1f305\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201023/OE3DVM6UYJE7NDWKYU76Z3HL5U/</a>"},{"pid":"c172040667e167c954fb8a8a800e3da9f4e75855","tid":2256651,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bbd102c7b8d3105e0abd02104872592e3c1e65","tid":2256651,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f457418a877c01cb3021a138706e91dd21d72be","tid":2256651,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"達哥：當然冇問題啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb20061cd988904ed5f5109233e4be6233cef689","tid":2256651,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:47:11.000Z"